WEBVTT

00:04:59.736 --> 00:05:03.400
I dok svakodnevno
proučavam Sunce i njegove oluje,

00:05:03.424 --> 00:05:07.350
uvijek ću duboko voljeti
ovaj predivan planet,

00:05:08.076 --> 00:05:09.547
iako samo blijeda plava točka,

00:05:09.547 --> 00:05:13.375
ali blijeda plava točka
koja ima nevidljivi magnetski štit

00:05:13.399 --> 00:05:15.605
koji nas čuva.

00:05:15.629 --> 00:05:16.935
Hvala vam.

00:05:16.959 --> 00:05:20.300
(Pljesak)